You know, the problem
really phrases like this--

00:26:10.910 --> 00:26:15.290
and if we had more time today,
I would sit and challenge you

00:26:15.290 --> 00:26:17.630
for five or 10 minutes
to go and think

00:26:17.630 --> 00:26:21.800
about how you take a pile of
cells from the early embryo

00:26:21.800 --> 00:26:23.660
and build that
structure, which could

00:26:23.660 --> 00:26:26.150
be what it is or
could be something

00:26:26.150 --> 00:26:28.450
that represents an organ.

00:26:28.450 --> 00:26:30.370
And while I'm moving
the boards, you

00:26:30.370 --> 00:26:33.520
