So I'm going to write
that the cells sort out.

00:27:33.620 --> 00:27:36.470
And there is a molecular
basis for that.

00:27:36.470 --> 00:27:39.370
It's called homotypic
adhesion, where

00:27:39.370 --> 00:27:41.960
like cells tend to
bind to one another,

00:27:41.960 --> 00:27:43.655
so that they can
function as a unit.

00:27:52.470 --> 00:27:57.240
But, of course, in order to
