OK.

00:28:08.220 --> 00:28:11.550
And they moved because
of their cytoskeleton,

00:28:11.550 --> 00:28:14.550
which was rearranging
and changing and allowing

00:28:14.550 --> 00:28:15.760
them to do so.

00:28:15.760 --> 00:28:18.390
So the molecular
basis for movement

00:28:18.390 --> 00:28:26.430
is cytoskeletal change
or rearrangement.

00:28:26.430 --> 00:28:28.680
What else is on my list?

00:28:28.680 --> 00:28:32.300
You know, the pile of
cells that I've got there,

00:28:32.300 --> 00:28:34.380
it's meant to look
