00:28:43.650 --> 00:28:45.990
Those cells are stuck together.

00:28:45.990 --> 00:28:48.100
And that is one of the
things that happens.

00:28:48.100 --> 00:28:50.295
The cells stick together.

00:28:53.560 --> 00:28:59.130
And they do so because of
cellular junctions, which

00:28:59.130 --> 00:29:01.920
are particular
collections of proteins

00:29:01.920 --> 00:29:03.940
that cause cells
to stick together,

00:29:03.940 --> 00:29:07.920
