00:29:35.360 --> 00:29:37.180
had a whole lecture on them.

00:29:37.180 --> 00:29:39.350
Cells can divide,
and they can die.

00:29:39.350 --> 00:29:41.210
You can get rid of
the excess cells.

00:29:41.210 --> 00:29:43.040
And you can generate
more cells to build

00:29:43.040 --> 00:29:52.130
your organ by the processes of
cell division and cell death.

00:29:52.130 --> 00:29:54.440
And we've had those
