00:30:31.970 --> 00:30:34.340
How do they know that
the dark blue ones

00:30:34.340 --> 00:30:37.670
are on the left and the columna
brown ones are on the right?

00:30:37.670 --> 00:30:38.990
It's a great question.

00:30:38.990 --> 00:30:41.070
And you know, if
we had more time,

00:30:41.070 --> 00:30:42.620
I think that the
thing would come up

00:30:42.620 --> 00:30:45.621
with was the notion
of some kind of plan,

00:30:45.621 --> 00:30:47.870
that there are instructions
somewhere that are telling

00:30:47.870 --> 00:30:49.460
the cells where to go.

00:30:49.460 --> 00:30:50.990
What are those instructions?

